subject: Second Vaccination and Questionnaire
message:
Dear Sir/Madam,

Your vaccination date for the second vaccination is the 15.7.2020. at 10:00-11:00.

 In the email is a questionnaire attached. Please fill it out in order for us to approve our service. https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeCmEgwkMCAuSOhKkT0Il6yv6861Jrtd-4sJO8ySLduytRf2g/viewform 

 The questionnaire is anonymous and all the data is being handled through strict GDPR guidelines. Thank you in advance and stay safe!

Kind regards,

GetShot team
